    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc208763n520as36856827857130">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>A letter to "My dear friend and pupil," January 25, 1841, telling of the death of his father-in-law. Inman tells his pupil he will not be able to give his usual lesson due to the funeral, and gives an at-home assignment instead.</p>
    </scopecontent>
